PLACEHOLDER — choose a licence before publishing.

The TDD suggests MIT or CC0, which also keeps any future vendored shader clean.
The PS1 shader (godot/addon/patina/ps1.gdshader) is written from scratch for
this project, so whatever you pick here covers it.

To use MIT, replace this file with the MIT licence text and your copyright line,
e.g.:

    MIT License
    Copyright (c) 2026 Brannen Graves / GabagoolStudios
    ...
